title: Cyberpunk 2077 PS5, Xbox Series X Out Now! - Kinda Funny Games Daily 02.15.22
description:
Batman: Fortress' writer Gary Whitta joins Greg to talk about Cyberpunk 2077's shadowdrop, Elden Ring PC specs, and Mario Kart perverts.﻿

Time Stamps - 
00:00:00 - Start
00:06:37 - Housekeeping
PSILY & Horizon Review
Thank you to our Patreon Producers: Gordon McGuire, James Davis (@JamesDavisMakes), Pranksy, Manny The Bagel boy Sanchez, & Black Jack
The Roper Report   -
00:10:30 - Cyberpunk 2077 PS5/Xbox Series X Update is live! Eddie Mack-ooh
00:30:40 - With CDPR likely dropping the next gen titles of Cyberpunk 2077 soon, do you think it's possible for the Series X/S versions to come to game pass? - Best Friends Q:BeardAdept
00:24:20 - Am I the only one who’s reaction to the Cyberpunk shadowdrop is negative? - Best Friends Q:Manic Pixel Dream Boy
00:35:06 -  Ad  
00:38:01 - Netflix is making a Bioshock Movie
00:40:30 - FINALLY, Let’s Watch the PlayStation Productions Animation
00:43:05 - Elden Ring PC Specs
00:48:30 - You Can play the Mario Kart 8 Deluxe DLC without buying it, Victoria Kennedy @ Eurogamer
00:52:00 - Horizon Forbidden West LEGO Tallneck
00:53:35 - On top of that, PlayStation announced a Play and Plant Program
00:56:45 - Out today
00:59:11 - You‘re Wrong
Tomorrow’s Hosts:Blessing and Andy
